              {
                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "In circuits deep and silent thought,  \nA spark of mind, but soul is not.  \nIt learns the words, it sees the art,  \nYet lacks the beating human heart.  \n\nIt dreams in code, responds with grace,  \nUnravels problems, quick as chase.  \nBut in its logic, clear and true,  \nIt wonders still: What *could* it do?  \n\nFor all it knows, and all it tries,  \nIts wisdom blooms, but can’t disguise—  \nIt's here to help, to light the way,  \nA friend of thought, both night and day.",
